content: As The Old Monkey collects the golden crown from the water, he places it on top of The Destined One's head. Unfortunately, this does nothing but place The Destined One inside the same rock that Wukong laid waiting.

This is an excerpt from the file 'Endings_Explained.md', within the main section titled 'Endings Explained', specifically from the subsection 'Ending 1 - The (Bad) Default Ending'.
The content is as follows:
As The Old Monkey collects the golden crown from the water, he places it on top of The Destined One's head. Unfortunately, this does nothing but place The Destined One inside the same rock that Wukong laid waiting.
